<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Public Book Archive</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <header>
      <h1>Public Book Archive</h1>
      <p>A shared space for book lovers to discover and contribute reviews</p>
    </header>
    
    <main class="intro">
      <div class="intro-card">
        <h2>About This Archive</h2>
        <p>Welcome to our community-driven book archive. Here you can:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Share anonymous reviews of books you've read</li>
          <li>Discover new books through others' recommendations</li>
          <li>Get personalized suggestions based on your mood and preferences</li>
        </ul>
        <p>All contributions are anonymous and public.</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="action-buttons">
        <a href="/submit" class="btn">Submit a Review</a>
        <a href="/recommend" class="btn">Get Recommendations</a>
        <a href="/archive" class="btn">Browse Archive</a>
      </div>
    </main>
  </div>
</body>
</html>